headline: Lululemon, Snowflake, Darden Restaurants: Top Analyst Calls
summary: Yahoo Finance senior reporter Brooke DiPalma keeps track of several Wall Street analyst calls on top trending stocks, including calls around shares of luxury athleisure brand Lululemon Athletica (LULU), cloud-based data platform Snowflake (SNOW), and Olive Garden parent company Darden Restaurants (DRI).
